OL,6,FA petition to stop the discos has
OL,7,Freached more than 1,600 signatures.
OL,9,FPetition organiser Cajetan Skowronski
OL,10,Fsaid: "It will not bring young people
OL,11,Fcloser to Christ, rather it will send
OL,12,Fthe message that Christ and his
OL,13,Fchurch, and all the truth, beauty and
OL,14,Fgoodness it has to offer, are
OL,15,Funimportant ` that entertainment
OL,16,Fdeserves our attention more than God,
OL,17,Fthat Christians do not take their
OL,18,Ffaith or their holy places seriously."
