OL,3,CCathedral defends silent discos
OL,4,Cagainst 'rave in nave' criticism
OL,6,F"Cathedrals have always been part of
OL,7,Fcommunity life in a way much wider
OL,8,Fthan their prime focus as centres of
OL,9,FChristian worship and mission, and
OL,10,Fwhether people choose to come to
OL,11,FCanterbury Cathedral primarily as
OL,12,Fworshippers, sightseers, or attendees
OL,13,Fat our events ` which include
OL,14,Fclassical concerts, light and sound
OL,15,Finstallations, and craft workshops `
OL,16,Fit's always joyous to see them
OL,17,Fdiscover this incredible place anew
OL,18,Fand on their own terms.
