OL,3,CCathedral defends silent discos
OL,4,Cagainst 'rave in nave' criticism
OL,6,F"Whilst dancing of all different kinds
OL,7,Fhas happened in the Cathedral over the
OL,8,Fcenturies - and The Bible memorably
OL,9,Fcelebrates the gift of dancing with
OL,10,FKing David dancing before the Lord (2
OL,11,FSamuel 6) ` there are many different
OL,12,Fviews on the secular and the sacred.
OL,14,F"Our 90s-themed silent disco will be
OL,15,Fappropriate to and respectful of the
OL,16,FCathedral ` it is categorically not a
OL,17,F'rave in the nave' - but I appreciate
OL,18,Fthat some will never agree that
OL,19,Fdancing and pop music have a place
OL,20,Fwithin cathedrals.
