OL,3,CCathedral defends silent discos
OL,4,Cagainst 'rave in nave' criticism
OL,6,F"I recently met and prayed with Mr
OL,7,FSkowronski who opposes the silent
OL,8,Fdisco and has called for it to be
OL,9,Fcancelled.
OL,11,F"Whilst we disagree in part about the
OL,12,Fnature of sacred space, we share the
OL,13,Fsame faith."
OL,15,FSilent discos at other cathedrals are
OL,16,Ftaking place later this month,
OL,17,Fincluding in Guildford, Ely and
OL,18,FChelmsford.
